Rewrapped - Season 2, Episode 8




Thin Mint Condition

Three Rewrappers are challenged to Recreate the refreshingly delicious Girl Scout Thin Mint cookie! One chef's use of raw sugar in their cookie dough leads to coarse reactions from the judges. In the Innovate Round, a Thin Mint-rubbed Duck Breast takes the snack to a whole new level! Who will be pinned the Rewrapped Winner? Find out on this minty fresh episode of Rewrapped!




Original Air Date: 01-Nov-2014
